import axios from "axios" import { useEffect, useState } from "react" export default function Users(){ function DelteUser(id){ axios.delete(`http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/user/delete${id}`) } const[Data,setData]=useState([]) useEffect(()=>{ fetch('http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/user/show') .then(res=>res.json()) .then(data=>setData(data)) }) const Maping=Data.map((user,index)=> {index} {user.name} {user.email} DelteUser(user.id)} className="fa-solid fa-trash" style={{color:"red",cursor:"pointer"}}> ) return( {Maping}
Id Users Email Acction
) }
